{
  "stem": "20218.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It's very hard to talk about it to me, but I saw they grabbed the children and threw it over the gate.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Because I was hidden in a attic, it was a little like, like a little light there, and I looked down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Every day, we were afraid we're going-- we're going to be taken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Finally, it took, I suppose-- I, I understood people were dying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They did-- they took the, the Jewish people was-- which had beards, they were religious people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They cut them off in the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They, they, they [? hit ?] them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It was-- it was very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then it came a big announcement that we all have to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know what the ghetto was, but it was outskirts of town, mostly Jewish populated and poor people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one by one, the buildings were marked to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did we go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Me and my brother, we had a little like carriage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We put-- whatever we could, we put in there because we couldn't take much with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Leave everything and go to ghetto, to those quarters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I remember, on the way, a lot of people were, were dying on the way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Me and my brother, we were still young.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother, my father, we all-- we all started to go to those quarters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of people, young people, they ran away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were on foot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They ran away to other par-- excuse me-- outer parts of the city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were-- they were trying to get to another country just away from, from Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father was in between them because they told him, you better go or you're going to get deported and shot anyway.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it took a day or two.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
